 Simple component with NS_DECL_ISUPPORTS and NS_IMPL_ISUPPORTS\n- nsAlertsService.h/cpp (toolkit/components/alerts/): Component implementing multiple interfaces (nsIAlertsService, nsIAlertsDoNotDisturb, nsIObserver) with observer pattern\n- AvailableMemoryWatcher.h/cpp (xpcom/base/): Demonstrates NS_DECL_NSIOBSERVER and Observe implementation for listening to system notifications\n- AudioChannelService.h/cpp (dom/audiochannel/): Shows NS_DECL_ISUPPORTS and NS_DECL_NSIOBSERVER usage in a complex component\n\nThe XPCOMComponentExample implements this exact pattern: a reference-counted component that observes system notifications through the observer service."
}

